creator: Mobi Softech
descriptionHtml:
My Invitation - Greetings is an app with latest customized invitations to start your every event with most professional way.

In this app there are more than 200 invitations with specific category like wedding, engagement, anniversary, housewarming, birthday, BBQ, Indian traditional invitations.

You can create or make your customized invitation in way you imagine in your mind. Also you have option to edit backgrounds.

We hope these templates & greeting cards will make your work more easier.

Hope you all satisfied with our app, Please leave your feedback.
